items.name: HackerRank-C-Programming
items.description: This repo contains solutions to nearly 200 advanced C exercises from my HackerRank course. Topics: variables, data types, control flow, sorting/searching algorithms, prime sieve, Fibonacci, file handling (TXT, binary), linked lists, structs, pointers, matrices, recursion. Explore for detailed solutions.
